"><p data-start="0" data-end="60">No problem. 😊 Let's do <strong data-start="24" data-end="47">just the first card</strong> very slowly.</p>
<h3 data-start="62" data-end="102">Step A: Find the Visualizations Pane</h3>
<p data-start="104" data-end="166">On the <strong data-start="111" data-end="125">right side</strong> of Power BI, you should see panels like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="168" data-end="207"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Data</span><br><span>Visualizations</span><br><span>Filters</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="209" data-end="252">If you don't see <strong data-start="226" data-end="244">Visualizations</strong>, click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="254" data-end="295"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>View → Panes → Visualizations</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="297" data-end="300">
<h3 data-start="302" data-end="327">Step B: Insert a Card</h3>
<p data-start="329" data-end="385">In the <strong data-start="336" data-end="354">Visualizations</strong> pane, click the <strong data-start="371" data-end="379">Card</strong> icon.</p>
<p data-start="387" data-end="401">It looks like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="403" data-end="418"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>123</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="420" data-end="466">A blank card will appear on the report canvas.</p>
<hr data-start="468" data-end="471">
<h3 data-start="473" data-end="498">Step C: Add Total AUM</h3>
<p data-start="500" data-end="534">In the <strong data-start="507" data-end="515">Data</strong> pane on the right:</p>
<ol data-start="536" data-end="634">
<li data-start="536" data-end="570">
<p data-start="539" data-end="570">Expand <strong data-start="546" data-end="570">03_aum_by_fund_house</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="571" data-end="592">
<p data-start="574" data-end="592">Find <strong data-start="579" data-end="592">aum_crore</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="593" data-end="634">
<p data-start="596" data-end="634">Drag <strong data-start="601" data-end="614">aum_crore</strong> onto the blank card</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="636" data-end="700">OR check the box next to <strong data-start="661" data-end="674">aum_crore</strong> after selecting the card.</p>
<p data-start="702" data-end="739">The card should now display a number.</p>
<hr data-start="741" data-end="744">
