<p data-start="17" data-end="88">In newer versions of Power BI, you may not immediately see <strong data-start="76" data-end="87">Maximum</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="90" data-end="99">Try this:</p>
<h3 data-start="101" data-end="113">Method 1</h3>
<p data-start="115" data-end="150">Click on the <strong data-start="128" data-end="149">Total Folios card</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="152" data-end="208">In the Visualizations pane, under <strong data-start="186" data-end="195">Value</strong>, you'll see:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="210" data-end="240"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9a8a5f2a.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>total_folios_crore</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="242" data-end="280">Click the small ▼ dropdown next to it.</p>
<p data-start="282" data-end="291">Look for:</p>
