<h3 data-start="213" data-end="225">Do this:</h3>
<p data-start="227" data-end="259">✅ Leave the line chart as it is.</p>
<p data-start="261" data-end="275">The task says:</p>
<blockquote data-start="277" data-end="307">
<p data-start="279" data-end="307">Industry AUM trend 2022–2025</p>
