<hr data-start="379" data-end="382">
<h2 data-start="384" data-end="420">Next: AUM by Fund House Bar Chart</h2>
<h3 data-start="422" data-end="432">Step 1</h3>
<p data-start="433" data-end="469">Click on a blank area of the canvas.</p>
<h3 data-start="471" data-end="481">Step 2</h3>
<p data-start="482" data-end="539">Click the <strong data-start="492" data-end="515">Clustered Bar Chart</strong> icon (horizontal bars).</p>
<h3 data-start="541" data-end="551">Step 3</h3>
<p data-start="552" data-end="557">Drag:</p>
