<hr data-start="225" data-end="228">
<h2 data-start="230" data-end="270">Step 2: Scatter Plot (Return vs Risk)</h2>
<h3 data-start="272" data-end="296">Insert Scatter Chart</h3>
<p data-start="298" data-end="331">Click the <strong data-start="308" data-end="325">Scatter Chart</strong> icon.</p>
<h3 data-start="333" data-end="347">Add Fields</h3>
